<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Payment Successful</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 28px;
      }
      .header .icon {
        font-size: 48px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }
      .content h2 {
        color: #333;
        margin-top: 0;
      }
      .payment-details {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .detail-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        margin: 10px 0;
        padding: 8px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
      }
      .detail-row:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #28a745;
      }
      .view-order-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 25px;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        transition: transform 0.2s ease;
      }
      .view-order-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }
      .info-box {
        background-color: #d1ecf1;
        border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px 30px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #6c757d;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .success-notice {
        background-color: #d4edda;
        border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
        color: #155724;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="icon">âœ…</div>
        <h1>Payment Successful!</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= firstName %>!</h2>
        <p>
          Great news! Your payment has been processed successfully on SmartPay. 
          Your order is now confirmed and will be processed shortly.
        </p>

        <div class="success-notice">
          <strong>Payment Confirmed:</strong> Your payment of <%= amount %> has been 
          successfully charged. Payment Method: <%= paymentMethod %>.
        </div>

        <div class="payment-details">
          <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #333;">Payment Details</h3>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span>Order Number:</span>
            <span><strong><%= orderNumber %></strong></span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span>Payment Date:</span>
            <span><%= paymentDate %></span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span>Payment Method:</span>
            <span><%= paymentMethod %></span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span>Payment Reference:</span>
            <span><%= paymentRef %></span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span>Total Paid:</span>
            <span><%= amount %></span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
          <strong>What happens next?</strong><br />
          Your order is now being prepared for shipment. You'll receive a shipping 
          confirmation email with tracking information once your items are on their way.
        </div>

        <p>Your order includes:</p>
        <ul>
          <% items.forEach(function(item) { %>
            <li><%= item.name %> - Quantity: <%= item.quantity %></li>
          <% }); %>
        </ul>

        <p>
          If you have any questions about your order or payment, please don't hesitate 
          to contact our customer support team.
        </p>

        <p>Thank you for choosing SmartPay!</p>
        <p><strong>SmartPay Team</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent to <strong><%= email %></strong></p>
        <p>
          Payment processed on <%= paymentDate %> | Order #<%= orderNumber %>
        </p>
        <p>
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> SmartPay. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>